OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FPerhaps rather cloudy to start,
OL,6,Fsoon clearing to give lengthy sunny
OL,7,Fspells. Cloud may linger near coasts.
OL,8,FWarm or very warm inland, cooler near
OL,9,Fcoasts especially in the strengthening
OL,10,Fwinds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FClear skies for most, except
OL,13,Fin the east and along the coast where
OL,14,Flow cloud will return and move inland,
OL,15,FWinds remain breezy and very gusty
OL,16,Falong the coast.
OL,17,
OL,18,CMonday:FAny cloud will quickly burn
OL,19,Foff to give sunny spells. Very warm,
OL,20,Fperhaps hot inland, but cooler near
OL,21,Fcoasts, in very breezy winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
