OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FLargely dry through this period, with
OL,7,Fcloud developing overnight then
OL,8,Fburning back to coasts by day to give
OL,9,Fsunny spells. Very warm, perhaps hot
OL,10,Finland, but cooler near coasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
